@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fssmdt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((v0 + 0.04 - tmp + 0.46)))
    v0 = 0.49
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.30 + v1 + 0.23) - (tmp + 0.93 - v0 + 0.25)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.01) * (v1 + 0.55 * v0 + 0.13)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
